{"word":"ἐρεθίζω","slug":"ἐρεθίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐρεϑίζω</el></b> [= <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Hom.\">Hom.</a> <el>ἐρέϑω</el> ‘provoke, trouble’] ‘rouse by challenging’, the more usual <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ neg.\">neg.</a> sense <b>vex, harass <a href='B:580 3:21'>Col 3:21</a>;</b> by rhetorical <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> in positive sense<b> challenge <a href='B:540 9:2'>2 Cor 9:2</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔργον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐρείδω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}